==Introduction==
''Euphoria'' is a song by [[じん]] and sang by IA.

This song is the theme song of the 30th IOI, while IA is also the mascot of the contest. {{Spoiler|This led to the contest being regarded as 肥宅快乐竞赛}}

== Lyrics ==
<poem>
その日、眺めていた校庭は
{{color|#00BFFF|薄く、青い空}}が染みていて
不意にガラン、とした教室に
君はもう、いなかった

